\c 9
\s Ezira anochema pamusoro pezvivi zvavanhu vake
\p
\v 1 Zvino izvi zvakati zvapera, machinda akaswedera kwandiri, akati: Vanhu VaIsraeri, navapristi, naVaRevhi havana kuzviraura pavanhu venyika panezvinonyangadza zvavo, ivo VaKenani, navaHiti, naVaPerezi, naVaJebhusi, naVaAmoni, navaMoabhu, naVaEgipita, naVaAmori.
\v 2 Nokuti vakatora vakunda vavo vave vakadzi vavo navavanakomana vavo; naizvozvo rudzi rutsvene rwakazvivenganisa navanhu venyika; zvirokwazvo maoko amachinda navabati ndiwo akanyanya pakudarika uku.
\p
\v 3 Zvino ini ndakati ndichizvinzwa, ndikabvarura nguvo yangu nejazi rangu, ndikataura vhudzi romusoro wangu nendebvu dzangu, ndikagara pasi ndakakanuka.
\v 4 Ipapo vakaungana kwandiri vese vakange vachidedera nokuda kwamashoko aMwari waIsraeri pamusoro pokudarika kwavatapwa; ndikagara pasi ndakakanuka kusvikira panguva yechipiriso chamadekwani.
\p
\v 5 Zvino panguva yechipiriso chamadekwani ndikasimuka pakuzvininipisa kwangu, ndichine nguvo yangu nejazi rangu zvakabvaruka; ndikawira pasi namabvi angu, ndikatambanudzira maoko angu kuna Jehovha Mwari wangu;
\v 6 ndikati: Haiwa, Mwari wangu, ndinonyara, ndinotsveruka kusimudzira chiso changu kwamuri Mwari wangu; nokuti zvivi zvedu zvadarika misoro yedu, mhosva yedu yakakwira kusvikira kudenga.
\v 7 Kubva pamazuva amadzibaba edu takapara mhaka kwazvo kusvikira nhasi; zvino nokuda kwezvivi isu namadzimambo edu, navapristi vedu, takaiswa mumaoko amadzimambo enyika, tiurawe nomunondo, titapwe, nokuparadzwa, nokunyadzwa, sapazuva ranhasi.
\v 8 Zvino takanzwirwa tsitsi naJehovha Mwari wedu nguva diki-diki, akatisiira vamwe vakapukunyuka, nokutipa mbambo panzvimbo yake tsvene, kuti Mwari wedu avhenekere meso edu, nokutiponesa padiki pauranda hwedu.
\v 9 Nokuti tiri varanda; kunyange zvakadaro Mwari haana kutirasi a pauranda hwedu, asi akatinzwisa tsitsi pamberi pamadzimambo ePerisia, akatiponesazve, kuti timutsezve imba yaMwari wedu, nokugadzira matongo ayo, nokutipa rusvingo paJudha napaJerusarema.
\v 10 Zvino Mwari wedu, tichareveiko shure kwaizvozvi? Nokuti takarasi a mirairo yenyu,
\v 11 yamakatiraira navaranda venyu vaporofita, muchiti: Nyika kwamunoenda, kuzoiita yenyu, inyika yakasvibiswa nokuipa kwavanhu venyika idzo, nemhaka yezvinonyangadza zvavo, zvakaizadza namatsvina avo kubva parutivi rumwe kusvikira panorumwe rutivi.
\v 12 Naizvozvo zvino, regai kupa vanakomana vavo vakunda venyu, kana kutora vakunda vavo kupa vanakomana venyu, kana kuvatsvakira rugare nomufaro nokusingaperi; kuti muve nesimba, mudye zvakanaka zvenyika, mugoisiira vana venyu ive nhaka yavo nokusingaperi.
\v 13 Zvatakaitirwa izvi zvese nokuda kwamabasa edu akaipa, uye nokuda kwemhosva dzedu huru, imwi Mwari wedu zvamusina kutirova zvakaringana zvakaipa zvedu, mukatisiira vamwe vakadai.
\v 14 Zvino tingapamhidzazve kudarika mirairo yenyu here, nokushamwaridzana navanhu vanoita izvi zvinonyangadza here? Hamungazotitsamwiri kusvikira matiparadza here, kusvikira kusina akasiiwa, kana akapukunyuka?
\v 15 Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri, imwi makarurama; nokuti tasiirwa vamwe vakapukunyuka, sezvazvakaita nhasi; tarirai tiri pamberi penyu nemhosva dzedu, nokuti hakuna angamira pamberi penyu nokuda kwechinhu ichi.